      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Sorry, we couldn’t find the page you’re looking for. It might have been moved, deleted, or you may have typed the URL incorrectly.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="mt-10 inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 text-white font-bold text-lg py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200">
        Go back home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
